          <article-title lang="original">중국 컴퓨터게임 소프트웨어 저작권보호의 주요쟁점 및 중국게임법의 개선방안 고찰</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">Legal Study on the China computer game software copyright protection and China game law</article-title>
          <article-title lang="english">Legal Study on the China computer game software copyright protection and China game law</article-title>
