          <article-title lang="original">게임이용자의 만족 성향이 게임 효능감에 미치는 영향 : PENS 척도를 중심으로</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">The Impact of Game User Satisfaction Tendencies on Game Efficacy : Focused on the PENS Scale</article-title>
          <article-title lang="english">The Impact of Game User Satisfaction Tendencies on Game Efficacy : Focused on the PENS Scale</article-title>
