          <article-title lang="original">한․중의 아시안게임과 문화정체성: 2010년 광저우아시안게임과 2014년 인천아시안게임을 중심으로</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">Korean Chinese Asian Games and Cultural Identity -Focused on 2010 Guangzhou and 2014 Incheon Asian Games-</article-title>
          <article-title lang="english">Korean Chinese Asian Games and Cultural Identity -Focused on 2010 Guangzhou and 2014 Incheon Asian Games-</article-title>
        </title-group>
