          <article-title lang="foreign">Regulation Risk and Implied Costs of Equity Capital in Game Industry: A Case of Game Shutdown</article-title>
          <article-title lang="english">Regulation Risk and Implied Costs of Equity Capital in Game Industry: A Case of Game Shutdown</article-title>
