          <article-title lang="foreign">The Influence of Cross Promotion in Mobile games on Consumer’s Attitude toward Game adoption</article-title>
          <article-title lang="english">The Influence of Cross Promotion in Mobile games on Consumer’s Attitude toward Game adoption</article-title>
