          <article-title lang="original">중국 온라인 게임 심의에 관한 규제 분석 -중국 NHN 게임을 중심으로-</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">The Analysis for the Regulation related to Chinese Online Game Review -Focused on NHN Chinese Game-</article-title>
