          <article-title lang="original">게임산업법상 사행성게임물 제도의 문제점에 관한 소고(小考)</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">On the Problems of the Korean Regulation on Gambling Games based on the Game Industry Act</article-title>
          <article-title lang="english">On the Problems of the Korean Regulation on Gambling Games based on the Game Industry Act</article-title>
        </title-group>
