          <article-title lang="original">「게임산업진흥에 관한 법률」의 게임물 사후관리 제도 개선방안 고찰</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">A Study on the Post-Management System of Game Rating in the Game Industry Promotion Act</article-title>
