          <article-title lang="original">게임내 광고의 효과성: 게임내 배너 및 빌보드 광고 사례 연구</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">How Effective Is In-Game Advertsing?: A Test Case of Hovorun's In-Game Banners and Billboards</article-title>
