        <title-group>
          <article-title lang="original">기획자를 위한 객체지향적 게임시스템 기획 방법</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">An Object-oriented Design Method of Game System for Game Designers</article-title>
          <article-title lang="english">An Object-oriented Design Method of Game System for Game Designers</article-title>
