        <title-group>
          <article-title lang="original">텍스트로서의 게임, 참여자로서의 게이머 : 디지털 게임의 문화연구적 접근</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">Game as a Text, Gamer as a Participant : A Cultural Studies' Approach to Digital Games</article-title>
