          <article-title lang="original">게임 캐릭터 인지성과 선호도에 관한 연구 -MMORPG 게임에서의 캐릭터를 중심으로-</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">A Study on Cognitive and Preference of Games’ Character -Focused on MMORPG Games' Character Design-</article-title>
          <article-title lang="english">A Study on Cognitive and Preference of Games’ Character -Focused on MMORPG Games' Character Design-</article-title>
