          <article-title lang="original">게임 데이터를 이용한 지표 개발과 승패예측모형 설계</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">Development of game indicators and winning forecasting models with game data</article-title>
          <article-title lang="english">Development of game indicators and winning forecasting models with game data</article-title>
        </title-group>
