          <article-title lang="original">게임 유저 유형에 따른 SCI 수준 및 게임 몰입도에 관한 연구</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">A Study on the Level of Self Character Identification and Game Flow according to Game User Type</article-title>
          <article-title lang="english">A Study on the Level of Self Character Identification and Game Flow according to Game User Type</article-title>
