          <article-title lang="original">교육용 게임을 플레이하려는 내적 동기 향상을 위한 전략 - 게임 디자인 이론을 중심으로</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">Design Strategies on Enhancing Intrinsic Motivation to Play Educational Games- Based on Game Design Theories</article-title>
          <article-title lang="english">Design Strategies on Enhancing Intrinsic Motivation to Play Educational Games- Based on Game Design Theories</article-title>
